        "/Noqa niyki qanta, \"Kallpachakuy,",
        "Wapuchakuypuni, Noqa qanwan kani./",
        "/Amapuni sayk’uychu, nitaj manchikuychu.",
        "Jehová Diosniyki qanwampuni kashani.”/"
